body:
I was just wondering if there was a way to tell the age of my account. I don't quite remember when I started playing but my earliest icon is from Season 2. However I was looking up S2 and I remember playing before that, even as early as beta. It might have just been a different account but It would be cool to know if this was my account carried from beta for all these years. I submitted a ticket but I was only directed to a....very undewhelming website for general stats and things. However I was able to learn my summoner ID so maybe someone would be willing to check into general timeframe (assuming they are generated in sequence) without me having to do a full written consent for simply the age of my account.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
A Very Thankful Player
